            "x1": 124,
            "y1": 169,
            "x2": 1574,
            "y2": 296
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 3,
        "text": "यह इतिहास अनूपम गाई । आगे कहों यसुपाई ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_13_textline_3.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 88,
            "y1": 738,
            "x2": 1725,
            "y2": 863
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 4,
        "text": "कोउ न मंत्र असदीन्ह समय नहीं सिय बसहिं बन ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_13_textline_4.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 230,
            "y1": 275,
            "x2": 1584,
            "y2": 389
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 5,
        "text": "चेरे पुर नर नारि शोचहिं व्याकुल जहँ सुनहिं ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_13_textline_5.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 240,
            "y1": 361,
            "x2": 1556,
            "y2": 477
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 6,
        "text": "यथा मीन बिन बारि तलफैं दोष लगाय विधि ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_13_textline_6.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 230,
            "y1": 450,
            "x2": 1561,
            "y2": 573
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 7,
        "text": "कौशल्यादि मातु उर शोचू । किमिकहिसकौंकहैंविधिबासु ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_13_textline_7.png",
