            "x1": 116,
            "y1": 541,
            "x2": 1693,
            "y2": 668
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 8,
        "text": "भयो देश पुर शोक निवासू । कहैं दीन प्रभुसिय बनबासु ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_13_textline_8.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 94,
            "y1": 637,
            "x2": 1696,
            "y2": 771
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 9,
        "text": "जब लक्ष्मण आये पहुंचाई । सभयविपिनप्रभुआयसुपाई ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_13_textline_9.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 86,
            "y1": 832,
            "x2": 1739,
            "y2": 960
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 10,
        "text": "पस्यो बुन्द जल घट मुखमाहीं । जागी सिय कहुं कोऊ नाहीं ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_13_textline_10.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 86,
            "y1": 918,
            "x2": 1696,
            "y2": 1053
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 11,
        "text": "अतिब्याकुलकरि रोदनभारी । हा लक्ष्मणतुमसमहितकारी ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_13_textline_11.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 88,
            "y1": 1009,
            "x2": 1701,
            "y2": 1147
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 12,
        "text": "क्यहि अपराध मोहिंतुमत्यागे । गयोअवध लखिसोवतभागे ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_13_textline_12.png",
